Title: Trouble at the Tree
Description:
$n! Merithra needs your help. 

Some nasty trickster spriggans followed us into the Dream and now they're causing all sorts of havoc!

Like the most important thing of all, stealing top secret super important supplies. 

It's urgent you stop them and get the supplies back.
ObjectivesText: Retrieve 6 Very Important Tree Supplies from Spriggans.
